<h4>
  Examples where parabolic motion is less obvious
</h4>

<ul>
  <li>An olympic archer's shot</li>
  <li>A 5-yard slant</li>
  <li>Spiking a volleyball</li>
  <li>Motion with lots of rotation, like throwing a wrenchin the air</li>
  <li>Human motion, such as a long jump or high jump</li>
</ul>

